node.text:
Making delicious “Pineapple Angel” cocktail with @lobos1707 and @chilledmagazine 
⠀
🍸
How to:
🍸
Cut fresh pineapple
Take a shaker and put 50g of fresh pineapple
Add 1/4 oz of sugar syrup
Muddle it
Squeeze fresh lime juice 3/4 oz
Add 4 sage leaves
Add 1 1/2 oz of @lobos1707 tequila
Add 3/4 oz of peach liqueur
 Add plenty of ice
Shake all ingredients
Fine strain into a chilled coupe glass
Garnish with sage
Enjoy!
🥃
Tag us in your story if you made it and have a wonderful day!
⠀
#allforthepack #chilled100 #nextlevelbartending
⠀

node.text:
Summer cocktail by Dwayne @therock Johnson - Ava-Colada
#CocktailsAtHome
🥑
Today we decided to recreate this delicious summer drink created by Dwayne Johnson
🥥
🥑
How to make this cocktail:
You will need shaker
Squeeze fresh lime juice
Add agave nectar
Add avocado 🥑
Muddle it
Add coconut 🥥 yogurt
Add tequila
Add plenty of ice
Shake everything
Pour into chilled glass with ice
And enjoy!
🥥
Let us know in the comments if you tried to make this drink, take a pics and tag us in your stories or posts 😊
We would like to see your creations!
🥑
Have a great day ! #nextlevelbartending #therock #avocado #tequila #tequilacocktails #coconut #cocktails #dwaynejohnson

node.text:
Visit our website for more cocktail recipes 😍
“Penicillin”
⠀
#CocktailsAtHome
🍸
How to:
🍸
You will need a shaker
Add blended scotch- 2 oz | 60 ml
Squeeze  lemon juice - 3/4 oz | 20ml
Add fresh ginger juice - 1/2 oz | 15 ml
Add honey syrup - 1/2 oz | 15 ml
Add ice and shake
Strain over ice into a chilled glass
Layer Islay single malt scotch - 1/4 oz | 10 ml
Garnish with candied ginger
Enjoy!
🥃
Tag us in your story if you made it and have a wonderful day!
⠀
#nextlevelbartending #penicillincocktail #scotchwhisky

Enjoy!
